        "eyebrow": "Our Story",
        "heading": "Why we built The BroBasket",
        "paragraph_1": "Most gift baskets are forgettable. A wicker basket. A red ribbon. Some no-name crackers and a tiny jar of jam. We've all sent one. We've all received one. Nobody talks about it the next day.",
        "paragraph_2": "We built BroBasket to fix that — for the dads, brothers, husbands, and friends who deserve a gift that actually lands. Real spirits. Real snacks. Real packaging that doesn't end up in the recycling on the way to the kitchen.",
